==English==

===Alternative spellings===
* (''Slang'') [[-in']] 

===Suffix===
'''-ing'''

# Used to form [[present participle]]s of [[verb]]s.
#:''making'' (as in ''You are making a mess.'')
# Used to form [[verbal noun]]s from verbs.
#:''making'' (as in ''The making of the film.'')
# Used for form [[uncountable]] nouns from various [[part of speech|parts of speech]] denoting materials or systems of objects considered collectively.
#:''roofing'' (''material for making or covering a roof'')
#:''piping'' (''system of pipes considered collectively'')

